DOC.brief_summary: The purpose study investigate effect EPA- DHA-enriched omega-3 polyunsaturated fatty acid dietary supplement cognitive function ( episodic memory , attention , work memory , executive function ) , subjective mood , alertness mental fatigue 26 week daily supplementation .
